(g) evidence of what compliance systems are used by the advice provider's
AFS licensee or authorised representative. This includes:
(i) training materials;
(ii) records of who is attending the training; and
(iii) call scripts; and
(h) evidence of how the advice provider has complied with these systems.
Note: This list is not intended to be exhaustive.
